, 120)\n})\n\ninput.onButtonPressed(Button.B, function () {\n    music.playMelody(\"G F E D C\", 120)\n})","README.md":"\n> Open this page at [https://plasnid.github.io/encoder-fun-v2/](https://plasnid.github.io/encoder-fun-v2/)\n\n## Use as Extension\n\nThis repository can be added as an **extension** in MakeCode.\n\n* open [https://makecode.microbit.org/](https://makecode.microbit.org/)\n* click on **New Project**\n* click on **Extensions** under the gearwheel menu\n* search for **https://github.com/plasnid/encoder-fun-v2** and import\n\n## Edit this project\n\nTo edit this repository in MakeCode.\n\n* open [https://makecode.microbit.org/](https://makecode.microbit.org/)\n* click on **Import** then click on **Import URL**\n* paste **https://github.com/plasnid/encoder-fun-v2** and click import\n\n#### Metadata (used for search, rendering)\n\n* for PXT/microbit\n<script src=\"https://makecode.com/gh-pages-embed.js\"></script><script>makeCodeRender(\"{{ site.makecode.home_url }}\", \"{{ site.github.owner_name }}/{{ site.github.repository_name }}\");</script>\n","pxt.json":"{\n    \"name\": \"encoder fun v2\",\n    \"description\": \"\",\n    \"dependencies\": {\n        \"core\": \"*\",\n        \"radio\": \"*\",\n        \"microphone\": \"*\",\n        \"ky040\": \"github:tinkertanker/pxt-rotary-encoder-ky040#v1.2.1\",\n        \"pxt-rb-joypi-advanced\": \"github:joy-it/pxt-rb-joypi-advanced#v1.0.9\"\n    },\n    \"files\": [\n        \"main.blocks\",\n        \"main.ts\",\n        \"README.md\"\n    ],\n    \"testFiles\": [\n        \"test.ts\"\n    ],\n    \"targetVersions\": {\n        \"branch\": \"v6.0.25\",\n        \"tag\": \"v6.0.25\",\n        \"commits\": \"https://github.com/microsoft/pxt-microbit/commits/f72136f1d01face3fc76caffa5343af1db369a37\",\n        \"target\": \"7.0.57\",\n        \"pxt\": \"9.0.15\",\n        \"targetId\": \"microbit\"\n    },\n    \"supportedTargets\": [\n        \"microbit\"\n    ],\n    \"preferredEditor\": \"tsprj\"\n}\n","t